Think about the tool-assisted
hunting at Fongoli,

00:54:22.940 --> 00:54:24.960
it perhaps can tell us more about some

00:54:24.960 --> 00:54:28.640
of the early hominin hunting
that went on compared

00:54:28.640 --> 00:54:32.550
to the emotionally-charged
hunting of chimpanzees,

